=== hoaxes ===
A threat/situation that doesn't actually exist
* May seem real but isn't
* Uses time & resources
* Forward email messages, printed memorandums etc.
* Often an email or wall post, tweet etc.
* Hoaxes can encourage you to spend money: Gift cards in particular
* Waste time by appearing as a virus

--- Protect against hoaxes ---
* Believe no one, consider the source
* Cross reference
* Confirm spam filter is working
* If it's too good to be true, don't fall for it
